class ResidualBlock(tf.keras.layers.Layer):
    def __init__(self, filters=1024, **kwargs):
        super(ResidualBlock, self).__init__(**kwargs)
        
        self.conv1 = tf.keras.layers.Conv2D(filters, kernel_size=3, strides=1, padding='same')
        self.norm1 = tf.keras.layers.BatchNormalization()
        self.relu1 = tf.keras.layers.ReLU()
        self.conv2 = tf.keras.layers.Conv2D(filters, kernel_size=3, strides=1, padding='same')
        self.norm2 = tf.keras.layers.BatchNormalization()
        self.relu2 = tf.keras.layers.ReLU()
        self.wise  = tf.keras.layers.Add()
        
    def call(self, x):
        r = x
        x = self.relu1(self.norm1(self.conv1(x)))
        x = self.relu2(self.norm2(self.conv2(x)))
        
        return self.wise([r, x])

def Generator():
    inputs = tf.keras.layers.Input(shape=(256, 256, 3))
    
    x = tf.keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size=7, strides=1, padding='same')(inputs)
    x = tf.keras.layers.BatchNormalization()(x)
    x = DownSample(128)(x)
    x = DownSample(256)(x)
    x = DownSample(512)(x)
    x = DownSample(1024)(x)
    x = ResidualBlock()(x)
    x = ResidualBlock()(x)
    x = ResidualBlock()(x)
    x = ResidualBlock()(x)
    x = ResidualBlock()(x)
    x = ResidualBlock()(x)
    x = ResidualBlock()(x)
    x = ResidualBlock()(x)
    x = ResidualBlock()(x)
    x = UpSample(512)(x)
    x = UpSample(256)(x)
    x = UpSample(128)(x)
    x = UpSample(64)(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.Conv2D(3, kernel_size=7, strides=1, padding='same')(x)
    
    return tf.keras.models.Model(inputs, [x, tf.keras.activations.tanh(x)])

def Discriminator():
    inputs = tf.keras.layers.Input(shape=(256, 256, 3))
    
    x = tf.keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size=4, strides=2, padding='same')(inputs)
    x = tf.keras.layers.LeakyReLU(0.2)(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.Conv2D(128, kernel_size=4, strides=2, padding='same')(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.BatchNormalization()(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.LeakyReLU(0.2)(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.Conv2D(256, kernel_size=4, strides=2, padding='same')(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.BatchNormalization()(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.LeakyReLU(0.2)(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.Conv2D(512, kernel_size=4, strides=2, padding='same')(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.BatchNormalization()(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.LeakyReLU(0.2)(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.Conv2D(512, kernel_size=4, strides=1, padding='same')(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.BatchNormalization()(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.LeakyReLU(0.2)(x)
    x = tf.keras.layers.Conv2D(1, kernel_size=4, strides=1, padding='same')(x)
    
    return tf.keras.models.Model(inputs, x)
